Package: affineModelR
Type: Package
Title: Affine Jump Diffusion Models for R
Version: 0.1
Date: 2016-01-21
Author: Piotrek Or{\l}owski, Andr{\'a}s Sali
Maintainer: Piotrek Or{\l}owski <first.last@gmail.com>
Description: Implementation of Duffie, Pan and Singleton's (2000) affine jump-
    diffusion framework for arbitrary number of factors and with elastic model
    specifications, with focus on equity applications. Evaluation of characteristic
    (moment generating) function and its derivatives by numerical solution of
    Riccati ODE system.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/piotrek-orlowski/affineModelR
Depends:
    deSolve,
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.1),
    RcppArmadillo
LinkingTo: Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
